00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:16.669 align:middle line:84%
It's actually OK to
receive something back.

00:07:16.669 --> 00:07:18.738 align:middle line:84%
And I believe, it doesn't
say anywhere in the Bible,

00:07:18.738 --> 00:07:20.407 align:middle line:84%
