and backgrounds, cultures,
colors, and creeds.

00:09:11.184 --> 00:09:14.988 align:middle line:84%
And, have you ever met
the person that said,

00:09:14.988 --> 00:09:17.457 align:middle line:84%
"I've set the goal
to be unhappy."

00:09:17.457 --> 00:09:18.258 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: No.

00:09:18.258 --> 00:09:19.125 align:middle line:90%
>> DM: No.

00:09:19.125 --> 00:09:20.026 align:middle line:84%
Didn't think so,
and this is you.

00:09:20.026 --> 00:09:21.694 align:middle line:90%
And they've been everywhere.

00:09:21.694 --> 00:09:23.129 align:middle line:84%
Well, neither have I
and I've traveled less

00:09:23.129 --> 00:09:24.531 align:middle line:90%
but neither have I.

00:09:24.531 --> 00:09:28.268 align:middle line:84%
So, what I accept therefore when
people set goals, they set goals

00:09:28.268 --> 00:09:32.138 align:middle line:84%
to be happy or happier
or more content.

00:09:32.138 --> 00:09:33.573 align:middle line:90%
So, that being said--

00:09:33.573 --> 00:09:34.641 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Or richer.

00:09:34.641 --> 00:09:36.075 align:middle line:84%
>> DM: Or richer,
yeah, all those things.

00:09:36.075 --> 00:09:39.946 align:middle line:84%
And that richness gives them
happiness, often of contentment,

00:09:39.946 --> 00:09:43.883 align:middle line:84%
or worthiness or self-esteem,
whatever, feelings of one end

00:09:43.883 --> 00:09:45.251 align:middle line:90%
or the other happiness.

00:09:45.251 --> 00:09:47.620 align:middle line:84%
But that's the challenge because
the problem with the goal,

00:09:47.620 --> 00:09:49.289 align:middle line:84%
doesn't matter if it's next
week, next month, next year,

00:09:49.289 --> 00:09:51.824 align:middle line:84%
or three years, five years,
10 years, it's future based.

00:09:51.824 --> 00:09:54.627 align:middle line:84%
As human beings, what we tend
to do is attach our happiness

00:09:54.627 --> 00:09:56.729 align:middle line:84%
or the contentment
to the achievements

00:09:56.729 --> 00:09:59.232 align:middle line:84%
of that future goal, and that's
where the happiness stays

00:09:59.232 --> 00:10:00.733 align:middle line:90%
which means you're not present.

00:10:00.733 --> 00:10:02.735 align:middle line:84%
The very act of setting
the goal, disconnects you

00:10:02.735 --> 00:10:04.237 align:middle line:84%
from who you are
now from your truth,

00:10:04.237 --> 00:10:06.105 align:middle line:90%
from your true self today.

00:10:06.105 --> 00:10:08.641 align:middle line:84%
So, you're on this
very, very long journey

00:10:08.641 --> 00:10:10.944 align:middle line:84%
and you can skip seeing your
happiness into the future.

00:10:10.944 --> 00:10:14.981 align:middle line:84%
But that's an illusion because
happiness is a now experience.

00:10:14.981 --> 00:10:16.015 align:middle line:90%
Happiness is not a thing--

00:10:16.015 --> 00:10:17.483 align:middle line:84%
well, you can't be
happy in the future.

00:10:17.483 --> 00:10:20.019 align:middle line:84%
We can only be happy now
because this is what we have.

00:10:20.019 --> 00:10:22.789 align:middle line:84%
So, when I begun to share
people about first begin to look

00:10:22.789 --> 00:10:24.457 align:middle line:84%
at the goals that
you're setting,

00:10:24.457 --> 00:10:26.326 align:middle line:84%
is it about setting
goals that bring you away

00:10:26.326 --> 00:10:29.362 align:middle line:84%
from your own oneness bring
you away from your true self.

00:10:29.362 --> 00:10:31.097 align:middle line:90%
Is that a wise thing to do?

00:10:31.097 --> 00:10:33.032 align:middle line:84%
And the question I mean,
sometimes tongue-in-cheek.

00:10:33.032 --> 00:10:35.368 align:middle line:84%
But I sometimes ask, well how
is it working out for you?

00:10:35.368 --> 00:10:37.437 align:middle line:84%
You know, how many years
you've been setting goals for?

00:10:37.437 --> 00:10:39.839 align:middle line:90%
Well, 10 or 30, you know.

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:42.809 align:middle line:84%
So, after 10, 20,
30 years, well,

00:10:42.809 --> 00:10:44.544 align:middle line:90%
how is that working out for you?

00:10:44.544 --> 00:10:46.479 align:middle line:84%
How is it working out
for your community?

00:10:46.479 --> 00:10:47.313 align:middle line:90%
For your business?

00:10:47.313 --> 00:10:48.781 align:middle line:90%
For the world?

00:10:48.781 --> 00:10:51.751 align:middle line:84%
We've all been doing this
for a hundred or more years.

00:10:51.751 --> 00:10:53.186 align:middle line:90%
But how is that working out?

00:10:53.186 --> 00:10:55.788 align:middle line:84%
Then we begin to be really
honest with ourselves and say,

00:10:55.788 --> 00:10:59.225 align:middle line:84%
maybe that our true self
doesn't get into the game.

00:10:59.225 --> 00:11:01.794 align:middle line:84%
Because setting our future
goals with this illusion

00:11:01.794 --> 00:11:04.397 align:middle line:84%
about happiness in the
future pulls us out,

00:11:04.397 --> 00:11:06.933 align:middle line:84%
cause that disconnect
and we cannot be present.

00:11:06.933 --> 00:11:09.168 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you don't bring your
best game into your business,

00:11:09.168 --> 00:11:11.504 align:middle line:84%
if you're not present in your
business, if your present

00:11:11.504 --> 00:11:13.773 align:middle line:84%
in word but not in deed,
in energy, in spirit,

00:11:13.773 --> 00:11:15.808 align:middle line:84%
'cause the best of you is
out there in some future,

00:11:15.808 --> 00:11:17.977 align:middle line:84%
how are you going to
help your clients?

00:11:17.977 --> 00:11:20.113 align:middle line:84%
How are you going to
change the world really?

00:11:20.113 --> 00:11:22.115 align:middle line:84%
So, people begun to
recognize the struggle

00:11:22.115 --> 00:11:25.318 align:middle line:90%
with bringing their A game,

00:11:25.318 --> 00:11:27.387 align:middle line:84%
their true self into
their business.

00:11:27.387 --> 00:11:30.256 align:middle line:84%
And so what we had to then do
was to discover there are ways

00:11:30.256 --> 00:11:32.125 align:middle line:84%
of bringing your true self
into the business and that's

00:11:32.125 --> 00:11:34.527 align:middle line:84%
by stop setting goals
'cause you people think

00:11:34.527 --> 00:11:35.662 align:middle line:84%
if you have a business,
you must set goals.

00:11:35.662 --> 00:11:37.330 align:middle line:90%
Well, to have a business,

00:11:37.330 --> 00:11:39.999 align:middle line:84%
it means about what you
decide to give as a service.

00:11:39.999 --> 00:11:42.035 align:middle line:84%
What's the passion
[inaudible] inside of you

00:11:42.035 --> 00:11:45.238 align:middle line:84%
and what are you going
to give as a service.

00:11:45.238 --> 00:11:47.907 align:middle line:84%
That brings us back to
we can keep ourselves--

00:11:47.907 --> 00:11:49.742 align:middle line:84%
what can we do to
keep ourselves true

00:11:49.742 --> 00:11:52.779 align:middle line:84%
in our self center
today, balance today?

00:11:52.779 --> 00:11:56.582 align:middle line:84%
And if we can find that place
and travel with that place

00:11:56.582 --> 00:11:59.652 align:middle line:84%
and energy inside of us and
bring it into the nine to five,

00:11:59.652 --> 00:12:02.789 align:middle line:84%
we can change the whole of
our responses in the world.

00:12:02.789 --> 00:12:04.624 align:middle line:90%
So, that was the first thing.

00:12:04.624 --> 00:12:06.926 align:middle line:84%
What was the second thing,
I'm not sure, I'm not sure.

00:12:06.926 --> 00:12:07.627 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Second.

00:12:07.627 --> 00:12:08.728 align:middle line:90%
>> DM: Second thing now.

00:12:08.728 --> 00:12:11.030 align:middle line:84%
So the other thing that
came to me was that,

00:12:11.030 --> 00:12:13.232 align:middle line:84%
you know when you
got this-- so I was--

00:12:13.232 --> 00:12:16.369 align:middle line:84%
I've been busy now building
business for 27 years.

00:12:16.369 --> 00:12:19.639 align:middle line:84%
And the problem with being busy
for those 27 years is 18 years

00:12:19.639 --> 00:12:21.074 align:middle line:84%
that were awful that
was really worse

00:12:21.074 --> 00:12:22.542 align:middle line:84%
and I was struggling
in business.

00:12:22.542 --> 00:12:25.078 align:middle line:84%
And-- man, this is
going to get my--

00:12:25.078 --> 00:12:27.013 align:middle line:84%
so, as I'm struggling
in business,

00:12:27.013 --> 00:12:30.983 align:middle line:84%
what's actually happening
is that I'm trying

00:12:30.983 --> 00:12:32.618 align:middle line:90%
to do the very best I can.

00:12:32.618 --> 00:12:36.856 align:middle line:84%
I'm giving everything I
can to customers, clients,

00:12:36.856 --> 00:12:39.726 align:middle line:84%
potential customers,
potential clients.

00:12:39.726 --> 00:12:42.095 align:middle line:84%
And as I do that,
they're winning.

00:12:42.095 --> 00:12:46.666 align:middle line:84%
They're getting benefits
but I'm losing.

00:12:46.666 --> 00:12:48.067 align:middle line:90%
Over the time, I began to share

00:12:48.067 --> 00:12:52.305 align:middle line:84%
and to experience myself was I
had to do what I call the A, B,

00:12:52.305 --> 00:12:56.209 align:middle line:84%
C, and C. Now, the A, B, C, and
C is just a really simple way

00:12:56.209 --> 00:12:59.278 align:middle line:84%
of saying, how'd you bring
your oneness into your business

00:12:59.278 --> 00:13:02.048 align:middle line:84%
and whether it really
accelerates you potential

00:13:02.048 --> 00:13:06.552 align:middle line:84%
to create wealth, to have more
money being your life 'cause you

00:13:06.552 --> 00:13:08.721 align:middle line:84%
can sit there attracting
but what are you going to do

00:13:08.721 --> 00:13:11.090 align:middle line:84%
to practically in your business
in the next meeting that you're

00:13:11.090 --> 00:13:12.725 align:middle line:84%
in to make sure that
more money comes to you

00:13:12.725 --> 00:13:15.628 align:middle line:84%
and that's what I call the A,
B, C, and C. And the A, B, C,

00:13:15.628 --> 00:13:18.464 align:middle line:84%
and C is actually really
straightforward because it's

00:13:18.464 --> 00:13:20.800 align:middle line:84%
about bringing your
authentic self

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:23.102 align:middle line:84%
into that business
every single day.

00:13:23.102 --> 00:13:25.538 align:middle line:84%
So, going back for one
moment for the goals,

00:13:25.538 --> 00:13:28.141 align:middle line:84%
if we detach ourselves
and put part of our self

00:13:28.141 --> 00:13:31.010 align:middle line:84%
into the future, it's difficult
to be our authentic self

00:13:31.010 --> 00:13:32.345 align:middle line:84%
in the present with
people that we sit

00:13:32.345 --> 00:13:33.546 align:middle line:90%
down we're hoping to serve.

00:13:33.546 --> 00:13:36.048 align:middle line:84%
So, it's not being really
authentic in that place.

00:13:36.048 --> 00:13:39.986 align:middle line:84%
I think that's the one that
people have first to recognize

00:13:39.986 --> 00:13:44.389 align:middle line:84%
that they must be fully present
with those they wish to serve.

00:13:44.389 --> 00:13:47.593 align:middle line:84%
The second part was around--
or the B is around the balance.

00:13:47.593 --> 00:13:49.796 align:middle line:84%
Because what was
instinct for me was that--

00:13:49.796 --> 00:13:53.966 align:middle line:84%
especially I'm coaching people
who are in business as coaches

00:13:53.966 --> 00:13:56.102 align:middle line:90%
and teachers and speakers.

00:13:56.102 --> 00:13:57.970 align:middle line:84%
And I would just say,
wow, this is interesting

00:13:57.970 --> 00:14:00.573 align:middle line:84%
because I think I love what you
do and I would say, you know,

00:14:00.573 --> 00:14:03.876 align:middle line:84%
and I love what you do and
you should be making a fortune

00:14:03.876 --> 00:14:05.178 align:middle line:90%
because you're giving a fortune

00:14:05.178 --> 00:14:06.813 align:middle line:84%
to the world through
what you do.

00:14:06.813 --> 00:14:08.247 align:middle line:90%
So what's happening?

00:14:08.247 --> 00:14:11.083 align:middle line:84%
And I remembered
where I came from.

00:14:11.083 --> 00:14:15.054 align:middle line:84%
Because the B in the A, B,
C, and C is not balance.

00:14:15.054 --> 00:14:18.791 align:middle line:84%
See at one end, if we are
martyrs, if we give everything

00:14:18.791 --> 00:14:21.727 align:middle line:84%
and give and give and give
and give in service and time

00:14:21.727 --> 00:14:24.964 align:middle line:84%
and energy to people,
eventually, we dissipate

00:14:24.964 --> 00:14:26.299 align:middle line:90%
that which we have, the gifts

00:14:26.299 --> 00:14:29.569 align:middle line:84%
that we have become
reduced and reduced.

00:14:29.569 --> 00:14:34.106 align:middle line:84%
And we can really help the
world, but it's about balance.

00:14:34.106 --> 00:14:37.210 align:middle line:84%
The other end of that
scale of balance is greed.

00:14:37.210 --> 00:14:39.979 align:middle line:84%
And if you're greedy, and
you think about just you,

00:14:39.979 --> 00:14:42.815 align:middle line:84%
what you can get, the money you
can make, then awfully that--

00:14:42.815 --> 00:14:44.784 align:middle line:84%
you may seem to win in the
short term, but we all know

00:14:44.784 --> 00:14:47.820 align:middle line:84%
that generates into you losing
the long term spiritually

00:14:47.820 --> 00:14:49.055 align:middle line:90%
or otherwise.

00:14:49.055 --> 00:14:51.490 align:middle line:84%
But if you're greedy, you're
thinking about yourself

00:14:51.490 --> 00:14:52.959 align:middle line:84%
and what you can get
and what you can charge

00:14:52.959 --> 00:14:54.961 align:middle line:84%
and how much money you can
make, but you know what?

00:14:54.961 --> 00:14:58.231 align:middle line:84%
When you're greedy, the world
suffers, those around you

00:14:58.231 --> 00:14:59.799 align:middle line:90%
and the world, they suffer.

00:14:59.799 --> 00:15:02.034 align:middle line:90%
But if we're martyrs, we suffer.

00:15:02.034 --> 00:15:03.569 align:middle line:90%
So, here's where we have to be.

00:15:03.569 --> 00:15:04.737 align:middle line:84%
We have to be here
in the middle.

00:15:04.737 --> 00:15:08.708 align:middle line:84%
It's OK to be a carpenter
and the son of God

00:15:08.708 --> 00:15:11.878 align:middle line:84%
or a great prophet or a
wise person or a spiritual

00:15:11.878 --> 00:15:15.982 align:middle line:84%
or a teacher, coach, mentor,
and to not be a martyr

00:15:15.982 --> 00:15:18.150 align:middle line:84%
to the world and
to not be greedy.

00:15:18.150 --> 00:15:19.719 align:middle line:84%
It's OK to have that
balance in the middle,

00:15:19.719 --> 00:15:23.522 align:middle line:84%
to accept that which is OK
for you to have accepted.

00:15:23.522 --> 00:15:25.925 align:middle line:84%
And when will that balance
placed, we [inaudible]

00:15:25.925 --> 00:15:28.828 align:middle line:84%
from being a martyr, and
people, potential customers

00:15:28.828 --> 00:15:31.063 align:middle line:84%
and clients pick up on
that energy and they go,

00:15:31.063 --> 00:15:32.531 align:middle line:90%
"I can't mess with this person.

00:15:32.531 --> 00:15:33.833 align:middle line:90%
I can't make them a martyr.

00:15:33.833 --> 00:15:36.736 align:middle line:84%
I was a martyr for 18 years
in my business driving all

00:15:36.736 --> 00:15:39.205 align:middle line:84%
over the UK for scraps of
business serving people

00:15:39.205 --> 00:15:41.007 align:middle line:90%
who woke up when they wanted."

00:15:41.007 --> 00:15:43.409 align:middle line:84%
I was suffering in pain and
working six days a week,

00:15:43.409 --> 00:15:45.544 align:middle line:84%
not until late into
the night as you know.

00:15:45.544 --> 00:15:50.082 align:middle line:84%
And I was the martyr, that's
not why I came here to be.

00:15:50.082 --> 00:15:51.851 align:middle line:84%
You know, I didn't come
here to be a martyr

00:15:51.851 --> 00:15:53.152 align:middle line:90%
to dissipate my energy.

00:15:53.152 --> 00:15:54.820 align:middle line:84%
It's fair for me to give
my service and my love

00:15:54.820 --> 00:15:56.122 align:middle line:90%
and my light to others.

00:15:56.122 --> 00:15:57.823 align:middle line:84%
But actually, it's OK for
me to have reward for myself

00:15:57.823 --> 00:15:59.258 align:middle line:90%
so that for me was OK.

00:15:59.258 --> 00:16:00.726 align:middle line:84%
I'm not a martyr
and I'm not greedy.

00:16:00.726 --> 00:16:04.230 align:middle line:84%
But then we have to look at
what's called the C in the A, B,

00:16:04.230 --> 00:16:08.367 align:middle line:84%
C and C. The C of this us that,
it's really interesting how

00:16:08.367 --> 00:16:12.672 align:middle line:84%
when we're in business,
that if you hear about,

00:16:12.672 --> 00:16:16.142 align:middle line:84%
you talk about energy and people
have heard you into before.

00:16:16.142 --> 00:16:20.346 align:middle line:84%
I love the fact that you meet
people who are most energetic

00:16:20.346 --> 00:16:23.049 align:middle line:90%
and enlightened and fun people.

00:16:23.049 --> 00:16:24.717 align:middle line:84%
Oftentimes when we're
in business

00:16:24.717 --> 00:16:28.454 align:middle line:84%
and we haven't got the rapport
with those with whom we wish

00:16:28.454 --> 00:16:34.327 align:middle line:84%
to serve, our high energy-- if
we're bouncing off the ceilings,

00:16:34.327 --> 00:16:37.396 align:middle line:84%
that high energy can put off
our opportunity to serve.

00:16:37.396 --> 00:16:39.832 align:middle line:90%
People just go, yeah.

00:16:39.832 --> 00:16:43.669 align:middle line:84%
Thank you, but not for me,
well, thank you very much.

00:16:43.669 --> 00:16:45.671 align:middle line:84%
So, we have to recognize
where they are.

00:16:45.671 --> 00:16:46.305 align:middle line:90%
It's not about us.

00:16:46.305 --> 00:16:47.707 align:middle line:90%
It's about them.

00:16:47.707 --> 00:16:50.343 align:middle line:84%
And it's also about saying if
our energy isn't high enough,

00:16:50.343 --> 00:16:53.546 align:middle line:84%
where enthusiasm isn't high
enough, we can also not--

00:16:53.546 --> 00:16:56.115 align:middle line:84%
we have some absolute
gems of wisdom

00:16:56.115 --> 00:16:57.817 align:middle line:84%
and really have the
ability to serve people,

00:16:57.817 --> 00:17:01.253 align:middle line:90%
have genius stuff inside of us.

00:17:01.253 --> 00:17:02.588 align:middle line:84%
But if our energy
isn't high enough,

00:17:02.588 --> 00:17:04.090 align:middle line:84%
or our [inaudible]
isn't high enough,

00:17:04.090 --> 00:17:07.893 align:middle line:84%
we also do not get the
ability or the right to serve.

00:17:07.893 --> 00:17:10.896 align:middle line:84%
So, when we look at the bouncing
off the walls and their energy,

00:17:10.896 --> 00:17:13.566 align:middle line:84%
we have to come back to the
center 'cause at the center

00:17:13.566 --> 00:17:15.501 align:middle line:84%
of all of us, you're
looking at balance

00:17:15.501 --> 00:17:17.570 align:middle line:90%
or looking at our energy.

00:17:17.570 --> 00:17:19.638 align:middle line:84%
We have to be balanced
and centered because back

00:17:19.638 --> 00:17:22.475 align:middle line:84%
to being the core, back to
being the true self 'cause

00:17:22.475 --> 00:17:24.377 align:middle line:90%
at the core, there's oneness.

00:17:24.377 --> 00:17:26.946 align:middle line:84%
At the core, there is the
oneness 'cause we're all part

00:17:26.946 --> 00:17:28.014 align:middle line:90%
of the oneness.

00:17:28.014 --> 00:17:30.149 align:middle line:84%
But also at the core
is our own oneness.

00:17:30.149 --> 00:17:31.584 align:middle line:90%
It's the part of the universe.

00:17:31.584 --> 00:17:35.688 align:middle line:84%
The part of the universe was
actually that came through me,

00:17:35.688 --> 00:17:38.524 align:middle line:84%
that came through you, that
come through each of us.

00:17:38.524 --> 00:17:40.860 align:middle line:84%
It's the light energy
that later you said,

00:17:40.860 --> 00:17:42.728 align:middle line:90%
the part of the universe is you.

00:17:42.728 --> 00:17:45.231 align:middle line:84%
But here's your personality
on it.

00:17:45.231 --> 00:17:46.332 align:middle line:90%
It's called your life.

00:17:46.332 --> 00:17:48.334 align:middle line:90%
A part of the universe is me.

